\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 7. Data handling, privacy and security\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 \'95 
\f0\b Data accessed:
\f1\b0  only the company's own campaign structures and performance metrics. No end-user personal data is retrieved through the API.\
\'95 
\f0\b Storage:
\f1\b0  API credentials (developer token, OAuth client, refresh token) are stored in a local, git-ignored configuration file on the owner's machine. Reports are stored locally for internal analysis only.\
\'95 
\f0\b No sharing or resale
\f1\b0  of any API data. No co-mingling with data from other advertisers (there are none).\
\'95 Website-side conversion tracking operates under a consent-management platform (Google Consent Mode v2) in compliance with EU/GDPR requirements.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 8. Compliance statement\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 \'95 The tool is an 
\f0\b internal-use tool for a single advertiser
\f1\b0  (the token holder's own company). It is not a third-party or full-service tool; accordingly, Required Minimum Functionality obligations for third-party tools do not apply. Should the tool's scope ever change, we will re-apply/notify Google as required.\
\'95 The tool will comply with the 
\f0\b Google Ads API Terms and Conditions
\f1\b0  and Google Ads policies, including the AI-generated content being subject to the same editorial review and policy checks as human-written ads (a human reviews all ad copy before it is submitted).\
\'95 Contact for API matters: contacto@aletopintores.com.\
